Package com.incadencecorp.coalesce.api

Contains APIs and supporting classes used by Coalesce

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CoalesceExim<T>
    Defines the interface for importing and exporting Coalesce Entities to other data formats.
    ICoalesceCache<K,T>
    Interface used for caching objects.
    ICoalesceComponent
    Every Synchronizer's API should extend this common interface.
    ICoalesceFieldDefinitionFactory
    This interface can be used to create definitions as needed.
    ICoalesceFieldEnumDefinitionFactory<T extends IFieldEnum>
    This interface extends ICoalesceFieldDefinitionFactory to include an additional generic method that uses the IFieldEnum.
    ICoalesceJob  
    ICoalesceMapper<T>
    This interface is used for mapping Coalesce types to other formats
    ICoalesceNormalizer
    Interface used for normalizing Coalesce objects to be used as keys.
    ICoalesceNotifier
    Interface for sending out notifications.
    ICoalescePersistorJob  
    ICoalescePopulator
    Interface for populating coalesce entities.
    ICoalescePrincipal
    This interface extends Principal to expose additional user's detail.
    ICoalesceResponseType<T>
    Interface that all tasks must implement.
    ICoalesceResponseTypeBase
    Interface that all jobs must implement.
    ICoalesceSetup
    Interface used by implementations that require addition setup before using.
    ICoalesceTargetJob<T>  
    IEnumerationProvider
    Defines the interface used by the enumeration field type for converting between integers and strings.
    IExceptionHandler
    This interface is used for creating handlers of exceptions.
    ISecurityRegistration<T extends CoalesceDataConnectorBase>
    This interface defines the methods required to register security settings to a given data base.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoalesceAttributes
    Defines attributes used through Coalesce
    CoalesceErrors
    Defines error messages used throughout Coalesce.
    CoalesceParameters
    Common Parameters
    ObjectFactory
    This object contains factory methods for each Java content interface and Java element interface generated in the com.incadencecorp.coalesce.api package.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EJobStatus
    Java class for EJobStatus.
    EResultStatus
    Java class for EResultStatus.
